        "rich_text_9hwRAc": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "11 Celebrity Engagement Rings That Define Modern Love | Bollywood Diamond & Platinum Trends",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h1>11 Celebrity Engagement Rings That Define Modern Love | Bollywood Diamond & Platinum Trends</h1>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "center"
          }
        },
        "follow_us_ygY8aG": {
          "type": "follow_us",
          "settings": {
            "header_title": "FOLLOW US ON",
            "header_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ccxpK9": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Introduction ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>They said “I do”, and the world paused to stare at the sparkle.</p><p>From the hush of a private proposal in Tuscany to the flash of paparazzi lights on a red carpet, celebrity engagements have a way of making us dream a little louder. </p><p>In Bollywood, every ring tells a story of love. individuality and evolving luxury. Today’s brides aren't chasing the biggest stone; they’re choosing meaning over magnitude and craftsmanship over cliche. Their rings reflect a generation that celebrates emotion as elegance, where a platinum solitaire ring can feel like a personal handwritten vow and a diamond engagement ring becomes a statement of both love and identity. </p><p>Here’s a closer look at 11 celebrity <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-ring\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"engagement rings\">engagement rings</a> that capture this new definition of forever, blending modern design, timeless craftsmanship and just the right amount of sparkle.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "center"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_kKqW7n": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1. Anushka Sharma’s Engagement Ring - Minimalist Luxury",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>1. Anushka Sharma’s Engagement Ring - Minimalist Luxury</h2>",
            "custom_id": "anushka",
            "text_alignment": "center"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_AynJ8F": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Anushka.png",
            "text": "<p>Anushka Sharma’s ring is everything her style has always been; effortless, graceful and quietly powerful. The round diamond ring with a subtle halo sits on a simple band, glowing every time it catches light.</p><p>Her choice sparked a whole wave of simple engagement rings, pieces that felt elegant effortlessly.</p><p>Lucira tip: For brides who love understated sparkle, a platinum round solitaire with a fine pave band offers brilliance that feels natural, not loud.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Jbd43L": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "2. Deepika Padukone’s Engagement Ring - The Platinum Statement",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>2. Deepika Padukone’s Engagement Ring - The Platinum Statement</h2>",
            "custom_id": "deepika",
            "text_alignment": "center"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_ACEyWj": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Deepika.png",
            "text": "<p>Deepika’s ring is exactly what you’d expect from her; poised, powerful and timeless. A platinum<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/solitaires\" target=\"_blank\" title=\" solitaire ring \"> solitaire ring </a>with a rectangular diamond that feels sculpted, like wearable architecture.</p><p>Lucira Tip: Platinum enhances clarity and stays white forever, a natural fit for women who live boldly but love quietly. </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_PYNpgj": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "3. Priyanka Chopra’s Engagement Ring - Tiffany’s Iconic Cushion Cut",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>3. Priyanka Chopra’s Engagement Ring - Tiffany’s Iconic Cushion Cut</h2>",
            "custom_id": "priyanka",
            "text_alignment": "center"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_TgFkLn": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Priyanka.png",
            "text": "<p>Nick Jonas literally shut down a Tiffany store of Priyanka’s ring and honestly the story never gets old. The<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/solitaires-cushion\" title=\" cushion cut solitaire\"> cushion cut solitaire</a>, framed by tapered baguettes. It’s classic yet global, much like her own journey.</p><p>Lucira Tip: Cushion cuts give off a soft, candlelight glow. Try it in platinum if you like cool sophistication, or rose gold for a touch of warmth.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ejh96n": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "4. Alia Bhatt’s Engagement Ring - The Girl-Next-Door Solitaire",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>4. Alia Bhatt’s Engagement Ring - The Girl-Next-Door Solitaire</h2>",
            "custom_id": "alia",
            "text_alignment": "center"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_gAYLKb": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Alia_bhatt.png",
            "text": "<p>At first glance, Alia Bhatt's ring seems beautiful and simple, a classic diamond solitaire on a delicate gold band. But look closer, you’ll find a story in detail. Her ring features an infinity symbol beneath the setting, a personal nod to Ranbir Kapoor’s lucky number and their promise forever. </p><p>Lucira Tip: Custom details, like hidden engravings or subtle symbols, turn a classic solitaire into something truly personal.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_eHiRME": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "5. Katrina Kaif’s Engagement Ring - A Royal Tanzanite Gemstone",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>5. Katrina Kaif’s Engagement Ring - A Royal Tanzanite Gemstone</h2>",
            "custom_id": "katrina",
            "text_alignment": "center"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_kjLWx6": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Katrina_a44eb4c9-dd29-4c2b-8454-88dcfb9690a3.png",
            "text": "<p>Katrina’s choice was refreshingly bold. Instead of a diamond, she went with a deep blue tanzanite stone surrounded by diamonds, regal striking and deeply personal. </p><p>Lucira tip: Colored stones like tanzanite or sapphire make perfect centerpieces for those who love jewelry that feels one of a kind.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_BWVmEe": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "6. Aditi Rao Hydari’s Engagement Ring - The Toi et Moi Symbol",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>6. Aditi Rao Hydari’s Engagement Ring - The Toi et Moi Symbol</h2>",
            "custom_id": "aditi",
            "text_alignment": "center"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_3q3M8G": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Aditi.png",
            "text": "<p>Inspired by the<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/toi-et-moi-engagement-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\" Toi et Moi \"> Toi et Moi </a>(“You and Me”) style, Aditi’s rumored ring celebrates two stones joined together symbolizing the meaning of equals. One shines with strength, the other with emotion; they stay together and create balance and harmony.</p><p>Lucira Tip: Combine contrasting cuts, a bold emerald and a soft pear, to capture your story in perfect symmetry.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bPLMNC": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "7. Kiara Advani’s Engagement Ring - The Oval Solitaire Trend",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>7. Kiara Advani’s Engagement Ring - The Oval Solitaire Trend</h2>",
            "custom_id": "kiara",
            "text_alignment": "center"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_wgriGb": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Kiara.png",
            "text": "<p>Kiara Advani’s <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-rings-oval\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"oval cut diamond solitaire\">oval cut diamond solitaire</a> is refined simplicity at its best. The elongated stone, set on a platinum band, flatters the hand and feels both timeless and now, much like her effortless charm.</p><p>Lucira Tip: Oval cuts offer a larger visual spread per carat, creating more brilliance and elegance with every moment.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_i8cP7e": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "8. Athiya Shetty’s Engagement Ring - Subtle & Chic",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>8. Athiya Shetty’s Engagement Ring - Subtle & Chic</h2>",
            "custom_id": "athiya",
            "text_alignment": "center"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_zwVAkV": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Image with Text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Athiya.png",
            "text": "<p>Athiya Shetty’s ring mirrors her understated sophistication. The round solitaire diamond on a sleek platinum band feels fresh, wearable, and unfailingly graceful. The kind of piece that ages beautifully with its wearer.</p><p>Lucira Tip: Platinum’s natural white hue complements round diamond perfectly, a match made for women who love quiet luxury.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_TbC4mN": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "9. Rakul Preet Singh’s Engagement Ring - A Radiant Choice",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>9. Rakul Preet Singh’s Engagement Ring - A Radiant Choice</h2>",
            "custom_id": "rakul",
            "text_alignment": "center"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_LPbVap": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Rakul.png",
            "text": "<p>Rakul Preet Singh’s radiant cut diamond brings together geometry and glow, the crisp lines of an emerald cut with the fire of round. It's modern, bold and full of movement, much like her personality.</p><p>Lucira Tip: The radiant cuts pair beautifully with pavé or baguette bands, giving dimension to their angular sparkle.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_hf4YDf": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "10. Genelia D’Souza’s Engagement Ring - Classic Romance",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>10. Genelia D’Souza’s Engagement Ring - Classic Romance</h2>",
            "custom_id": "genelia",
            "text_alignment": "center"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_NwRy9R": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Image with Text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Genelia.png",
            "text": "<p>Genelia D’souza’s<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-rings-round\" target=\"_blank\" title=\" round diamond engagement ring\"> round diamond engagement ring</a> feels like a love letter when in light, a four prong platinum solitaire that's effortlessly timeless. It's the kind of ring you wear everyday and never tire of it. </p><p>Lucira Tip: the round solitaire on platinum is still one of the most loved ring designs for women, classic, versatile, and forever elegant</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_VkJeEq": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "11. Sonam Kapoor’s Engagement Ring - The Fashion Icon’s Pear-Cut Diamond",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>11. Sonam Kapoor’s Engagement Ring - The Fashion Icon’s Pear-Cut Diamond</h2>",
            "custom_id": "sonam",
            "text_alignment": "center"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_iiFrKE": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Image with Text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/7_8912f9a5-5de4-4b6e-92bc-9f662ef18fcb.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Sonam kapoor’s pear shaped diamond engagement ring captures her spirit perfectly, bold, avant-garde, and full of sentiment. The tear drop shaped sparkles with emotion and artistry, reflecting a woman who sets trends instead of following them.</p><p>Lucira Tip: Pear cuts flatter every hand and symbolise tears of joy, an ideal choice for brides who lead with both passion and style.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_CbXLkg": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Bollywood's Modern Love Language: The Platinum Revolution",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Bollywood's Modern Love Language: The Platinum Revolution</h2><p>Across all these stories, one detail quietly steals the spotlight is “Platinum.”</p><p>More than just a metal, it has become a symbol of strength, purity and permanence. From diamond wedding rings for women to platinum solitaire rings, this trend shows modern brides value meaning over flash.</p>",
            "custom_id": "bollywood",
            "text_alignment": "center"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_3fBN74": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion</h2><p>From Anushka’s quiet grace to Sonam’s fearless sparkle, Bollywood’s engagement rings remind us that every love story shines differently. Beyond the glamour and the flashbulbs are stories of real emotion, of love that feels personal, modern, and deeply true.</p><p>At Lucira, every piece is designed to become part of your story, timeless in beauty, personal in meaning, and forever yours.</p>",
            "custom_id": "conclusion",
            "text_alignment": "center"
          }
        }
